{"tid":437703,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[真女神] Jessica演唱會因颱風取消　親到會場跳《Fly》氹粉絲","createTime":"2017-10-16T08:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T10:40:55.000Z","uid":38407,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c23c2af278397e2c7b9192bb6f2dd47dacec0f77","tid":437703,"uid":38407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"今年真係特別多8號風球，仲要3次都撞正星期日掛8號，放假先嚟打風！尋日（10月15日）香港又因為受到颱風「卡努」吹襲，掛8號風球掛足全日，本來呢一日係前少女時代成員Jessica喺香港舉辦演唱會嘅日子，最終都因為「卡努」而遺憾取消，令好多金星（Jessica粉絲名稱）都好失望！不過Jessica似乎知道粉絲嘅心意，呢一晚就為粉絲準備咗驚喜！<br />\n<br />\n攝影：特約記者<br />\nJessica親自去到會場同粉絲道歉，又同大家傾偈，補償大家冇得睇騷嘅遺憾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/907600/xlarge/0bbdfcc8a75fdfec358030df14e96efe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F907600%2Fxlarge%2F0bbdfcc8a75fdfec358030df14e96efe.jpg&h=1a7bc716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（觀看更多）<br />\n<br />\n少女時代前成員Jessica到港　勁親民同粉絲揮手<br />\n雖然演唱會宣布取消，但不少粉絲已經冒住風雨去到九展Star Hall，Jessica知道知後決定臨時現身會場見大家，主辦方亦發布消息通知粉絲，Jessica大概晚上時現身Star Hall門口，當時現場已經有逾300名粉絲守候，Jessica一出場粉絲就立即起哄大嗌：「Jessica！Jessica！」，又大合唱佢嘅歌曲《Fly》，Jessica亦配合地跳起《Fly》舞步，十足搞迷你粉絲見面會一樣！<br />\nJessica見到粉絲都好開心，最後仲同粉絲大合照先離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/907601/xlarge/86aa86b5c435869c2938f0acdd2fd9ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F907601%2Fxlarge%2F86aa86b5c435869c2938f0acdd2fd9ea.jpg&h=15e732c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（觀看更多）<br />\n<br />\n韓星姊妹出發米蘭時裝周　Krystal拎未定價手袋Jessica愛BVLGARI<br />\n由於現場並冇準備到咪，Jessica唯有大聲用英文同粉絲傾偈，佢仲為演唱會取消一事向大家道歉，但現場嘅粉絲都大嗌：「It&rsquo;s OK！」Jessica唔單止同粉絲道歉，仲留低同全場粉絲合照，留足10分鐘先肯離開！呢晚嚟到會場嘅粉絲真係好多，所以Jessica要走勻Star Hall嘅兩邊門先可以見齊兩批粉絲，不過Jessica轉場期間粉絲都跟住衝過去，情況有啲混亂，幸好最後冇粉絲受傷。"},{"pid":"be304fac742ca15febc83fdaafb0b2e5a634e77d","tid":437703,"uid":38407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk01.kpop/videos/1388544171258338/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk01.kpop%2Fvideos%2F1388544171258338%2F&d=Ui2P69gUQGZudWyCemU58DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ff200c2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk01.kpop/videos/1388544171258338/</a><br />\n人美心更美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d896bc5c61e17a361c696a9956e37243efc38a","tid":437703,"uid":38407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/907625/xlarge/4eb80feb27328f7cc2850f6e06196ddd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F907625%2Fxlarge%2F4eb80feb27328f7cc2850f6e06196ddd.jpg&h=cacf0e48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/907620/xlarge/fbcee1fc2b764eb4d7a0a979ec16752a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F907620%2Fxlarge%2Ffbcee1fc2b764eb4d7a0a979ec16752a.jpg&h=2022b86c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/907627/xlarge/6cda40f4b9c241988c797c477abccce9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F907627%2Fxlarge%2F6cda40f4b9c241988c797c477abccce9.jpg&h=aa61103d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0e65a673b121fc2840c5235dd212b0f7044e351","tid":437703,"uid":38407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/126120/thumbnail/f9d70a45baff752c6f6db594048f5de0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F126120%2Fthumbnail%2Ff9d70a45baff752c6f6db594048f5de0.jpg&h=ffd9c76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/907622/xlarge/cc1941d2264c9eaf90f88311cd2bc366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu